    "description": "Supertech Ventures Solutions is actively seeking a talented and motivated Business Development Manager to join our dynamic team in Bhubaneswar. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Supertech Ventures Solutions:\nSupertech Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Supertech Ventures Solutions!",
